text:
500 ml bottle

Aroma: bakery yeast and alcohol, nutty toffee, bananas and bubble gum, smidgen of caramel and a touch of resin; 

Appearance: Hazy amber colour, huge light brown head, swiss cheese consistency, dissipates slowly, foamy lacing;

Taste: sweet and bitter;

Palate: Full bodied, sticky texture, mild carbonation and sticky very slightly astringent finish;

Overall: Very robust and complex.
